@startuml
title Diagrama de secventa - Modul Client (Punctele c si d)

actor Client as C
participant "UI_Meniu" as UI
participant "PopUpLegislativ" as PopUp
participant "CosCumparaturi" as Cos
participant "ArticolCos" as Articol
participant "ProdusMeniu" as Produs
participant "ComandaService" as Comanda

== Subpunctul d) Pop-up Legislativ ==
C -> UI : apasaButonInfo(produs)
activate UI
UI -> PopUp : afiseazaPopUp(produs)
activate PopUp

PopUp -> Produs : getIngrediente()
Produs --> PopUp : ingrediente
PopUp -> Produs : isVegetarian()
Produs --> PopUp : boolean
PopUp -> Produs : isPicant()
Produs --> PopUp : boolean

PopUp --> UI : afisare informatii
deactivate PopUp
UI --> C : vede pop-up
deactivate UI

== Subpunctul c) Adaugare in Cos ==
C -> UI : adaugaInCos(produs, cantitate)
activate UI
UI -> Cos : adaugaInCos(produs, cantitate)
activate Cos

Cos -> Produs : isDisponibil()
Produs --> Cos : true

alt produsul exista deja in cos
    Cos -> Cos : adaugaCantitate(cantitate)
else e produs nou
    Cos -> Articol ** : new ArticolCos(produs, cantitate)
end

Cos --> UI : succes
deactivate Cos
UI --> C : actualizare vizuala
deactivate UI

== Legatura cu Subpunctul e) Plasare Comanda ==
C -> UI : plaseazaComanda()
activate UI
UI -> Cos : plaseazaComanda()
activate Cos

Cos -> Cos : calculeazaTotal()
Cos -> Comanda : creeazaComanda(elemente)
Comanda --> Cos : OK
Cos -> Cos : golesteCos()

Cos --> UI : comanda plasata
deactivate Cos
UI --> C : afiseaza chitanta
deactivate UI

@enduml